<br>
Leave the buffing to the support classes.<br>
<br>
I want to be considered as a viable source of sustained DPS in exp grinds. Equivalent to a reasonably equipped rogue at the same level.<br>
<br>
Whether that means better innate mana regen, higher damage nukes, lowering mana cost of existing nukes, or whatever else, is up to the devs to figure out.<br>
<br>
Along with that, I'll accept a drastic reduction to my ability to solo.  Take my snare, even take my needlessly abundant root spells if you want.<br>
<br>
What I don't want is some line of utility spells to maintain the exp-group-damage-comes-from-melee-classes-only status quo.<br>
<br>
<br>
